		<title>天体周围引力场和 Birkhoff 定理</title>
		<link>http://multiverse.lamost.org/blog/4090</link>
		<comments>http://multiverse.lamost.org/blog/4090#comments</comments>
		<pubDate>Sat, 06 Oct 2012 15:58:20 +0000</pubDate>
